===Glyph origin===
{{Han etyl}}
{{Han compound|ls=ic|單|犬|t1=hunting weapon|t2=dog}} – "hunting". {{lang|zh|口}} was added later (see {{lang|zh|[[嘼#Glyph_origin|嘼]]}}).

===Etymology===
Exopassive of {{och-l|狩|to hunt}}, literally "what is hunted" ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Speculatively, {{och-l|獸}} can be compared with {{cog|bo|འཆོར་བ||to hunt}} ({{zh-ref|ibid.}}).

